title Streaming Response Handling\n<size:11>ChatCmplStreamHandler.handle_stream() — accumulate tokens, detect tool calls, emit events, finalize response</size>

|#E8F4FD| Caller / Stream Source |
|#F0FFF0| ChatCmplStreamHandler |
|#FFF8E1| StreamingState |
|#FDE8F0| Event Consumer |

|ChatCmplStreamHandler|
start
:Initialize **StreamingState**\n(started=False, empty accumulators)\nInitialize **SequenceNumber** counter;

|StreamingState|
note right
  Fields:
  • started, thinking_text/signature
  • text/refusal/reasoning_content_index_and_output
  • function_calls, function_call_streaming
  • function_call_output_idx, provider_data
end note

|ChatCmplStreamHandler|
while (async for **chunk** in AsyncStream?) is (chunk received)

    if (state.started == False?) then (yes — first chunk)
        :Set state.started = True;
        |Event Consumer|
        :yield **ResponseCreatedEvent**\n(response, type="response.created");
        |ChatCmplStreamHandler|
    endif

    if (chunk.usage is not None?) then (yes)
        |StreamingState|
        :Update usage accumulator\n(prompt_tokens, completion_tokens);
        |ChatCmplStreamHandler|
    endif

    if (no chunk.choices OR no delta?) then (yes — empty chunk)
        :skip → **continue** to next chunk;
    else (no — has delta)

        |StreamingState|
        :Update **provider_data**\n(model from chunk or param,\nresponse_id from chunk.id);
        |ChatCmplStreamHandler|

        '--- BRANCH A: Anthropic Thinking Blocks ---
        if (delta.thinking_blocks exists?\n<size:10>[Anthropic via LiteLLM]</size>) then (yes)
            |StreamingState|
            :Accumulate **state.thinking_text** += block["thinking"]\nStore **state.thinking_signature** = block["signature"];
            |ChatCmplStreamHandler|
        endif

        '--- BRANCH B: OpenAI-style Reasoning Summary ---
        if (delta.reasoning_content exists?\n<size:10>[OpenAI o-series]</size>) then (yes)
            if (First reasoning_content chunk?\nstate.reasoning_content_index_and_output is None?) then (yes)
                :Create **ResponseReasoningItem**\n(id=FAKE_ID, summary=[], type="reasoning");
                |StreamingState|
                :Set reasoning_content_index_and_output = (0, reasoning_item);
                |ChatCmplStreamHandler|
                |Event Consumer|
                :yield **ResponseOutputItemAddedEvent**\n(output_index=0);
                |ChatCmplStreamHandler|
            endif
            if (active_reasoning_summary_index is None?) then (yes — new summary segment)
                :Append Summary(text="") to reasoning_item.summary\nSet active_reasoning_summary_index;
                |Event Consumer|
                :yield **ResponseReasoningSummaryPartAddedEvent**\n(summary_index, part);
                |ChatCmplStreamHandler|
            endif
            |StreamingState|
            :Accumulate reasoning_item.summary[index].text\n+= reasoning_content;
            |ChatCmplStreamHandler|
            |Event Consumer|
            :yield **ResponseReasoningSummaryTextDeltaEvent**\n(delta=reasoning_content);
            |ChatCmplStreamHandler|
        endif

        '--- BRANCH C: 3rd-Party Reasoning Text ---
        if (delta.reasoning exists?\n<size:10>[DeepSeek / other providers]</size>) then (yes)
            if (First reasoning chunk?\nstate.reasoning_content_index_and_output is None?) then (yes)
                :Create **ResponseReasoningItem**\n(content=[Content(text="", type="reasoning_text")]);
                |StreamingState|
                :Set reasoning_content_index_and_output = (0, reasoning_item);
                |ChatCmplStreamHandler|
                |Event Consumer|
                :yield **ResponseOutputItemAddedEvent**\n(output_index=0);
                |ChatCmplStreamHandler|
            endif
            |StreamingState|
            :Accumulate reasoning_item.content[0].text\n+= delta.reasoning;
            |ChatCmplStreamHandler|
            |Event Consumer|
            :yield **ResponseReasoningTextDeltaEvent**\n(delta=reasoning_text);
            |ChatCmplStreamHandler|
        endif

        '--- TRANSITION: Close open reasoning summary before other content ---
        if (Reasoning active AND open summary segment AND\nnew content/refusal/tool_calls arriving?) then (yes)
            :_finish_reasoning_summary_part();
            |Event Consumer|
            :yield **ResponseReasoningSummaryPartDoneEvent**;
            |StreamingState|
            :Reset active_reasoning_summary_index = None;
            |ChatCmplStreamHandler|
        endif

        '--- BRANCH D: Regular Text Content ---
        if (delta.content is not None?) then (yes)
            if (First text chunk?\nstate.text_content_index_and_output is None?) then (yes)
                :Compute content_index\n(0 + reasoning_offset + refusal_offset)\nCreate **ResponseOutputText**(text="")\nCreate **ResponseOutputMessage**(status="in_progress");
                |StreamingState|
                :Set text_content_index_and_output = (index, output_text);
                |ChatCmplStreamHandler|
                |Event Consumer|
                :yield **ResponseOutputItemAddedEvent**\n(output_index = 0 or 1 based on reasoning);
                :yield **ResponseContentPartAddedEvent**\n(part=ResponseOutputText);
                |ChatCmplStreamHandler|
            endif
            :Convert logprobs via ChatCmplHelpers;
            |StreamingState|
            :Accumulate text_output.text += delta.content\nAppend logprobs;
            |ChatCmplStreamHandler|
            |Event Consumer|
            :yield **ResponseTextDeltaEvent**\n(delta=delta.content, logprobs);
            |ChatCmplStreamHandler|
        endif

        '--- BRANCH E: Refusal Content ---
        if (delta.refusal exists?\n<size:10>[OpenAI — not all providers set this]</size>) then (yes)
            if (First refusal chunk?\nstate.refusal_content_index_and_output is None?) then (yes)
                :Compute refusal_index\n(reasoning + text offsets)\nCreate **ResponseOutputRefusal**(refusal="")\nCreate **ResponseOutputMessage**(status="in_progress");
                |StreamingState|
                :Set refusal_content_index_and_output = (index, output_refusal);
                |ChatCmplStreamHandler|
                |Event Consumer|
                :yield **ResponseOutputItemAddedEvent**;
                :yield **ResponseContentPartAddedEvent**\n(part=ResponseOutputRefusal);
                |ChatCmplStreamHandler|
            endif
            |StreamingState|
            :Accumulate refusal_output.refusal += delta.refusal;
            |ChatCmplStreamHandler|
            |Event Consumer|
            :yield **ResponseRefusalDeltaEvent**\n(delta=delta.refusal);
            |ChatCmplStreamHandler|
        endif

        '--- BRANCH F: Function / Tool Calls ---
        if (delta.tool_calls exists?) then (yes)
            :For each **tc_delta** in delta.tool_calls;
            if (tc_delta.index NOT in state.function_calls?) then (yes — new tool call)
                |StreamingState|
                :Create ResponseFunctionToolCall\n(arguments="", name="", call_id="")\nSet function_call_streaming[index] = False;
                |ChatCmplStreamHandler|
            endif
            |StreamingState|
            :Accumulate function_calls[index].arguments\n+= tc_function.arguments\nSet .name from tc_function.name;
            :Set .call_id from tc_delta.id\n<size:10>(Gemini: ChatCmplHelpers.clean_gemini_tool_call_id\nremoves __thought__ suffix)</size>\nCapture thought_signature\nfrom provider_specific_fields / extra_content;
            |ChatCmplStreamHandler|
            if (NOT yet streaming AND\nname AND call_id both known?) then (yes — begin streaming)
                :Compute output_index\n(reasoning + text + refusal + prior streaming calls)\nMark function_call_streaming[index] = True\nStore function_call_output_idx[index];
                |Event Consumer|
                :yield **ResponseOutputItemAddedEvent**\n(item with empty arguments, output_index);
                |ChatCmplStreamHandler|
            endif
            if (Streaming active AND tc_function.arguments?) then (yes)
                |Event Consumer|
                :yield **ResponseFunctionCallArgumentsDeltaEvent**\n(delta=tc_function.arguments);
                |ChatCmplStreamHandler|
            endif
        endif

    endif

endwhile (stream exhausted)

'============================================================
' POST-STREAM FINALIZATION
'============================================================
partition "**Post-Stream Finalization**" {

    :Call **_finish_reasoning_item()**;
    note right
      If summary reasoning:
        → yield ResponseReasoningSummaryPartDoneEvent
        → reset active_reasoning_summary_index
      If 3rd-party reasoning:
        → yield ResponseReasoningTextDoneEvent
      Always:
        → yield ResponseOutputItemDoneEvent (reasoning)
        → Set reasoning_item_done = True
    end note

    if (state.text_content_index_and_output?) then (yes)
        |Event Consumer|
        :yield **ResponseContentPartDoneEvent**\n(part = accumulated ResponseOutputText);
        |ChatCmplStreamHandler|
    endif

    if (state.refusal_content_index_and_output?) then (yes)
        |Event Consumer|
        :yield **ResponseContentPartDoneEvent**\n(part = accumulated ResponseOutputRefusal);
        |ChatCmplStreamHandler|
    endif

    :For each **function_call** in state.function_calls;
    if (function_call_streaming[index] == True?) then (yes — was streamed)
        |Event Consumer|
        :yield **ResponseOutputItemDoneEvent**\n(item with full arguments);
        |ChatCmplStreamHandler|
    else (no — fallback: name never arrived mid-stream)
        |Event Consumer|
        :yield **ResponseOutputItemAddedEvent**\nyield **ResponseFunctionCallArgumentsDeltaEvent**\n(delta = all accumulated arguments)\nyield **ResponseOutputItemDoneEvent**;
        |ChatCmplStreamHandler|
    endif

    :Build **outputs** list:\n[ reasoning_item?, assistant_message?, ...function_calls ];

    if (state.thinking_text?) then (yes — Anthropic)
        |StreamingState|
        :Attach thinking_text → reasoning_item.content\nAttach thinking_signature → reasoning_item.encrypted_content;
        |ChatCmplStreamHandler|
    endif

    if (text or refusal content accumulated?) then (yes)
        :Create final **ResponseOutputMessage**\n(status="completed", content=[text?, refusal?]);
        |Event Consumer|
        :yield **ResponseOutputItemDoneEvent**\n(assistant message, output_index=0 or 1);
        |ChatCmplStreamHandler|
    endif

    :Build **final_response** = response.model_copy()\nSet output = outputs\nSet usage = ResponseUsage\n(input_tokens, output_tokens, total_tokens,\nreasoning_tokens, cached_tokens);
    |Event Consumer|
    :yield **ResponseCompletedEvent**\n(response=final_response, type="response.completed");
    |ChatCmplStreamHandler|
}

stop

note bottom
  **Provider Compatibility Notes:**
  • OpenAI: standard chunks, usage in last chunk
  • LiteLLM: may omit chunk.usage; delta.refusal may be absent
  • Anthropic (via LiteLLM): thinking_blocks on delta; signature in encrypted_content
  • Gemini (via LiteLLM): tool_call.id has __thought__ suffix → cleaned; thought_signature in provider_specific_fields / extra_content
end note

@enduml
